title: 10 - A Totally Different Way to Date with JP Pokluda
description:
Single friends - this episode is for you. My friend JP led a ministry of singles for over 10 years and this conversation about dating will surprise you! Join us and get ready to take notes.

You HAVE to read JP's new book 'Outdated' available now: https://www.amazon.com/Outdated-Find-Lasts-Dating-Changed/dp/080109495X
